            . I had him in charge, and some persons attempted to rescue him.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I was working in Whitecross-street, and going to get my supper, as I passed the yard the gentleman ran out and collared me; a woman told them at the time. that I was not the thief.</p>
